OL,3,C'Probably worst days for Muslim
OL,4,Ccommunity'
OL,6,FThe violence and intimidation of
OL,7,Frecent days in parts of Belfast has
OL,8,Fput a sharper focus on how Northern
OL,9,FIreland deals with the problem of
OL,10,Fracism.
OL,12,FBusinesses have been destroyed and
OL,13,Flives have been left in turmoil, after
OL,14,Fsimmering racism spilled out onto the
OL,15,Fstreets.
