OL,3,C'Probably worst days for Muslim
OL,4,Ccommunity'
OL,6,FWhile for many people from ethnic
OL,7,Fminority backgrounds the problem is
OL,8,Fnothing new, one member of the Muslim
OL,9,Fcommunity who moved here from Iraq
OL,10,Fover 30 years ago, has told UTV these
OL,11,Fare the worst days he's ever
OL,12,Fexperienced.
OL,14,F"People are scared, people don't know
OL,15,Fwhat to do," Dr Raied Al-Wazzan from
OL,16,Fthe Belfast Islamic Centre said.
OL,18,F"These are probably the worst days the
OL,19,FMuslim community have ever seen in
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
