OL,3,C'Probably worst days for Muslim
OL,4,Ccommunity'
OL,6,F"Luckily the vast majority of people
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland are welcoming and
OL,8,Fsupportive and we've been inundated
OL,9,Fwith a huge number of messages of
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,F"But we need politicians to take the
OL,13,Flead, to put a plan in place on how to
OL,14,Ftackle these issues, and we are
OL,15,Fwilling to help."
OL,17,FIn west Belfast there was a
OL,18,Fcelebration of diversity - a chance
OL,19,Ffor different nationalities to come
OL,20,Ftogether.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
