OL,3,C'Probably worst days for Muslim
OL,4,Ccommunity'
OL,6,FBut the scenes of recent days remain
OL,7,Fat the forefront of people's minds.
OL,9,FGlen Phillips said: "I've spoken to
OL,10,Fmany people in the Holyland area who
OL,11,Fare now walking down the street
OL,12,Flooking both ways, not venturing out
OL,13,Fafter dark.
OL,15,F"Sometimes it may be an unfounded fear
OL,16,Fand sometimes it may not be, but it
OL,17,Fhas really impacted on how people are
OL,18,Fliving their lives."
OL,20,FFor some here through, the welcome has
OL,21,Fbeen and continues to be warm.
