OL,6,FRasha Salis added: "I have a lot of
OL,7,Flocal friends, they ask me 'do you
OL,8,Fneed help, do you need anything, do
OL,9,Fyou need groceries - we are here'.
OL,11,F"I feel very comfortable because I
OL,12,Fhave a lot of Irish people here, local
OL,13,Ffriends."
